Finding
=======

# metacharacters
. * \ [ ^ $

# special functions (when escaped)
+ ? | & { ( ) /

\t = tab
\s = whitespace
\n = newline
\r = carriage return

# repetition
\{#}

e.g. a\{2} matches aa

# backreferences
\(foo\)

Replacing
=========

\r = newline
\n = null byte (0x00)
\& = ampersand
\0 = inserts the text matched by the entire pattern
\1 = inserts the text matched by the first backreference (\2 etc)
